## Watchdog count semantics note

The T7 medium goal's abort condition #4 counts watchdog restarts across the
whole batch. Currently at 10 (the abort threshold). After this classifier
extension lands, the operator still needs to decide before resuming T7 medium:
- Reset the watchdog count to 0 for the new batch (treat as session-scoped), OR
- Raise the threshold to 20, OR
- Investigate Pentagon's poller stress under sustained load.

This decision is OUT OF SCOPE for the classifier extension and belongs in
the T7 medium resume goal.
